# kriegerdataforge-portfolio — Cursor rules

The canonical agent guide for this repo is **AGENTS.md**. Read [`AGENTS.md`](./AGENTS.md) first —
it covers the repo's vision & purpose, tech stack, module map, critical rules, and required reading.

For every task, follow:

- [`WORKFLOW.md`](./WORKFLOW.md) — the tiered task workflow (Quick / Standard / Epic; plan → owner
  approves → implement → `make ci` green → PR → GitHub CI green → owner merges).
- [`skills.md`](./skills.md) — the security playbook (read before any security-sensitive work).
